EMWM is a lightweight window manager for X11. It is derived from MWM, adding
support for UTF-8, Xinerama and Extended Window Manager Hints.

Libraries and Headers required for building:

libx11 
libxt
libxext
libxft
libxrandr
libxinerama
libxm (open-motif/motif)

EMWM is built with an ordinary makefile. Following variables may need to be
overridden depending on system/user preferences:
PREFIX (defaults to /usr), MANDIR, MWMRCDIR, APPLRESDIR

Run 'make', then 'make install' as root.
